<br>
The spell description states that it reduces your aggro by 30%.  Maybe it doesn't change your aggro at all.  Maybe it simply acts as a temporary aggro reducer while the spell is in effect.  So whatever your aggro was before, subtract 30% for the life of the spell.  Then once the spell is finished, your aggro returns to what it was.  <br>
